casebody.data:
Dedrick H. Bultman, Respondent v. The New York Elevated Railroad Company, et al., Appellants. Decided January 11, 1892. Appeal by defendants from judgment entered at special term. Davies & Rapallo, for appellants. Peckham & Tyler, for respond-dent.

Before Freedman, P. J., McAdam and Gildersleeve, JJ.

Per Curiam.

Judgment affirmed, with costs.
